{
  "texts": [
    "As with HPE, object detection and tracking (ODT) has a significant presence in sports broadcasting, for similar reasons.",
    "Unlike HPE, solutions are not prescribed on a case-bycase basis.",
    "Rather they tackle implicit issues given a set of idiomatic environment characteristics (Kaushal et al. 2018).",
    "For example for football, we could envision a method for detecting a ball in motion within a noisy environment.",
    "This translates well to other sports with similar tropes, such as handball."
  ]
}